snippet.title: The Boys - Final Season Teaser Trailer | Prime Video
snippet.description:
This is the teaser trailer for The Boys Season 5. It‚Äôs Homelander‚Äôs world, completely subject to his erratic, egomaniacal whims. Hughie, Mother‚Äôs Milk, and Frenchie are imprisoned in a ‚ÄúFreedom Camp.‚Äù Annie struggles to mount a resistance against the overwhelming Supe force. Kimiko is nowhere to be found. But when Butcher reappears, ready and willing to use a virus that will wipe all Supes off the map, he sets in motion a chain of events that will forever change the world and everyone in it. It‚Äôs the climax, people. Big stuff‚Äôs gonna happen April 8 on Prime.

¬ª Watch The Boys on Prime Video: https://amzn.to/2SQdfsv
¬ª SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/PrimeVideoSubscribe

About The Boys:
THE BOYS is an irreverent take on what happens when superheroes, who are as popular as celebrities, as influential as politicians and as revered as Gods, abuse their superpowers rather than use them for good. It's the powerless against the super powerful as The Boys embark on a heroic quest to expose the truth about ‚ÄúThe Seven,‚Äù and their formidable Vought backing.
 
About Prime Video:

snippet.description:
India‚Äôs Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas ‚Äî ‚ÄòSholay - The Final Cut‚Äô 12th Dec release worldwide

Presenting the trailer of Sholay: The Final Cut.
Restored in 4K & Dolby 5.1, and releasing on 12th December 2025, this is the first-ever theatrical presentation of the original uncut version. As we celebrate 50 years of Sholay, we are honoured to bring this timeless classic back to cinemas for audiences old and new.

Produced by Sippy Films ¬∑ Directed by Ramesh Sippy ¬∑ Restored by Film Heritage Foundation
Releasing theatrically via PEN Marudhar.

#SholayTheFinalCut #SholayOn12Dec #SholayTrailer

Film cast : Amitabh Bachchan, Dharmendra, Hema Malini, Sanjeev Kumar, Amjad Khan, Jaya Bachchan, A K Hangal, Satyen Kappu, Mac Mohan, Sachin Pilgaonkar, Jagdeep, Asrani, Leela Mishra, Iftekhar, Om Shiv Puri, Viju Khote, Vikas Anand, Keshto Mukherjee, Mushtaq Merchant, Gita Siddharth, Helen, Jalal Aga, Birbal, Jairaj, Master Alankar, Raj Kishore, Sharad Kumar, Bhanumati, Rajesh, Darshan, Rajan Kapoor, Habib, Surender, Bhagwan Sinha, Jerry Dsouza, Kedar, Saigal, Rajeshwari, Krishna, Girija

Film Director : Ramesh Sippy
Film Producer : G P Sippy

 In the village of Ramgarh, retired police chief Thakur Baldev Singh (Sanjeev Kumar) plots to bring down the notorious bandit Gabbar Singh (Amjad Khan) and enlists the help of two lesser criminals, Jai (Amitabh Bachchan) and Veeru (Dharmendra). When Gabbar attacks the village, however, Jai and Veeru wonder why Thakur does nothing to help them. They soon learn that he has no arms, and that Gabbar was the one who cut them off. Enraged by this, they redouble their efforts to help.

India‚Äôs Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas ‚Äî ‚ÄòSholay - The Final Cut‚Äô 12th Dec release worldwide

Presenting the trailer of Sholay: The Final Cut.
Restored in 4K & Dolby 5.1, and releasing on 12th December 2025, this is the first-ever theatrical presentation of the original uncut version. As we celebrate 50 years of Sholay, we are honoured to bring this timeless classic back to cinemas for audiences old and new.

Produced by Sippy Films ¬∑ Directed by Ramesh Sippy ¬∑ Restored by Film Heritage Foundation
Releasing theatrically via PEN Marudhar.

Singer : Anand Bakshi, Bhupinder, Kishore Kumar, Lata Mangeshkar, Manna Dey, R D Burman
Lyricist : Anand Bakshi
Music Director : R D Burman, Basu Manohari, Maruti Rao
Film Director : Ramesh Sippy
Film Producer : G P Sippy

 In the village of Ramgarh, retired police chief Thakur Baldev Singh (Sanjeev Kumar) plots to bring down the notorious bandit Gabbar Singh (Amjad Khan) and enlists the help of two lesser criminals, Jai (Amitabh Bachchan) and Veeru (Dharmendra). When Gabbar attacks the village, however, Jai and Veeru wonder why Thakur does nothing to help them. They soon learn that he has no arms, and that Gabbar was the one who cut them off. Enraged by this, they redouble their efforts to help.

üî• The Final Clash of Week 1! FFMAI 2025 BR Play-Ins Day 3 is HERE! üî•

Two days of relentless battles have led to this! It‚Äôs the final showdown of the Play-Ins week at the Free Fire MAX Asia Invitational 2025!

This is where the dream ends for some and begins for others:

The leaderboard is taking shape. By the end of today, only the Top 10 teams will survive to join the 8 Seeded Teams in the Main Event. For the rest, the journey ends here. There are no second chances‚Äîit‚Äôs qualify or go home.

Today, Group A takes on Group C in a fight for the final crucial points.

Playing Today:
Group A: NG PROS, GODLIKE ESPORTS, THE GOAT ESPORTS, GOW ESPORTS, BANGLADESH TOP 1, IQOO OGxTSG.
Group C: AVIDA x KDC, GB ESPORTS, META NINZA, REVENANT XSPARK, FANGS, IQOO RECKONING.

The cheers will roar, the pressure will be immense, and the final 10 qualifiers will be decided today.

18 Teams. 10 Qualifying Spots. The final fight for the Main Event begins NOW! üëë

snippet.title: Jallad | Official Trailer | Take A Break Horror Specials
snippet.description:
This Trailer gives a thrilling sneak peek into our upcoming horror comedy special where 4 friends visit an abandoned villa for a fun getaway‚Ä¶ but end up waking the angry ghost of a Jallad. What starts as masti, teasing and vacation vibes quickly turns into chaos, jump scares, and hilarious panic as the group tries to escape from the terrifying spirit who is determined to hunt them down.

üîî Watch the full trailer, and stay tuned for the complete horror comedy movie ‚Äî because darr bhi hoga, hassi bhi hogi!

snippet.description:
üî• PETTAI TV EXCLUSIVE ‚Äî ‚ÄúKANDHAN MALAI‚Äù TRAILER FULL REACTION + DEEP INVESTIGATION

In this detailed PETTAI TV episode, we present the most comprehensive reaction and factual decoding of the newly released Kandhan Malai trailer featuring BJP leader H. Raja.
This is not a simple reaction video ‚Äî it is a complete breakdown that exposes the propaganda patterns, political messaging, communal triggers, and historical distortions embedded within the trailer.

‚∏ª

üé¨ What This Video Does ‚Äî In FULL Detail (Line-by-Line, Scene-by-Scene Decode)

üîπ 1. Scene-by-scene explanation of communal triggers

We examine every dialogue, visual cue, and symbolic reference that seems designed to provoke:
 ‚Ä¢ Anti-Muslim undertones
 ‚Ä¢ Anti-Dravidian political messaging
 ‚Ä¢ Selective and exaggerated depictions of violence
 ‚Ä¢ Attempts to rewrite social justice history
 ‚Ä¢ Demonisation of specific communities

We show how these scenes follow known propaganda templates used across India in recent years.

‚∏ª

üîπ 2. Religious ownership narrative ‚Äî EXPOSED

A major section of the trailer claims that Thirupparankundram Hill ‚Äúbelongs only to one religion‚Äù.
In our video, we clearly explain:
 ‚Ä¢ The actual recorded history of the hill
 ‚Ä¢ Why the claim is factually wrong
 ‚Ä¢ The historical presence of Sikandar Auliya Dargah
 ‚Ä¢ How multi-faith heritage has existed for hundreds of years
 ‚Ä¢ How the trailer tries to erase this shared identity

We provide documented evidence, old records, and references to existing court documents.

‚∏ª

üîπ 3. Emanuel Sekaran, Pasumpon, Muthuramalinga Thevar ‚Äî Why these names matter politically

The trailer includes emotionally charged references to these leaders.
We explain:
 ‚Ä¢ Why using these names carelessly can trigger community tensions
 ‚Ä¢ Past clashes between the communities
 ‚Ä¢ How this film seems to re-open old wounds
 ‚Ä¢ Why this is extremely dangerous for Tamil Nadu

We highlight how cinema is being used to play psychological games with caste identities.

‚∏ª

üîπ 4. Dravidian movement portrayal ‚Äî FACT CHECKED

The trailer claims:
‚ÄúDravidian parties taught caste‚Äù

We show why this is false, with:
 ‚Ä¢ Historical data
 ‚Ä¢ Government orders
 ‚Ä¢ Social justice milestones
 ‚Ä¢ Reservation policies
 ‚Ä¢ Caste upliftment reforms
 ‚Ä¢ Achievements of DMK, Periyar, Anna, M. Karunanidhi, M.K. Stalin

We expose how the trailer hides 2,000 years of caste oppression and selectively blames only the last few decades.

‚∏ª

üîπ 5. Temple‚ÄìMosque‚ÄìChurch control narrative ‚Äî FULL TRUTH

The trailer says ‚ÄúTemples should not be in government control.‚Äù
We expose the selective outrage:
 ‚Ä¢ Temples in Maharashtra, Odisha, MP, AP, Karnataka ‚Äî all under government control
 ‚Ä¢ BJP rules/ruled most of these states
 ‚Ä¢ Yet the ‚Äúanti-government control‚Äù argument is raised only in Tamil Nadu
 ‚Ä¢ This exposes political targeting, not genuine religious concern

We show documented proof.

‚∏ª

üîπ 6. Women-shaming scenes ‚Äî Why they are toxic

We highlight the scenes that:
 ‚Ä¢ Insult women‚Äôs choices
 ‚Ä¢ Mock love, marriage, inter-caste relationships
 ‚Ä¢ Reinforce patriarchal views
 ‚Ä¢ Misrepresent well-known cases like Udumalpet Shankar‚ÄìKausalya

We explain how such portrayals fuel honour killings and caste politics.

‚∏ª

üîπ 7. Pattern of propaganda ‚Äî How the trailer fits a national template

We decode:
 ‚Ä¢ Visual tone
 ‚Ä¢ Background score style
 ‚Ä¢ Hero-villain framing
 ‚Ä¢ Threat manufacturing
 ‚Ä¢ Slogan repetition techniques
 ‚Ä¢ Emotional triggers
 ‚Ä¢ Selective historical edits

We show how this follows the ‚ÄúNorth India model of polarisation‚Äù that has caused violence in several states.

‚∏ª

üîπ 8. FULL deconstruction of how UP-style communal politics is being imported into Tamil Nadu

We explain step-by-step:
 ‚Ä¢ How communal fear is manufactured
 ‚Ä¢ How ‚Äúenemy images‚Äù are created
 ‚Ä¢ Why certain groups are demonised
 ‚Ä¢ How false claims become political weapons
 ‚Ä¢ Why Tamil Nadu is being targeted
 ‚Ä¢ How such films try to create clash-driven narratives

We expose the machinery behind this.

Kandhan malai troll
‚∏ª

üòÇ Comedy + Awareness ‚Äî PETTAI TV Style
Even though this is a serious subject, we deliver it with:
 ‚Ä¢ Humour
 ‚Ä¢ Satire
 ‚Ä¢ Reaction faces
 ‚Ä¢ Punch dialogues
 ‚Ä¢ Sharp editing

The aim:
Make people laugh ‚Üí Make them think ‚Üí Make them aware.

‚∏ª

In this detailed PETTAI TV episode, we present the most comprehensive reaction and factual decoding of the newly released Kandhan Malai trailer featuring BJP leader H. Raja.

Cricket Live


When: Saturday, December 6, 2025 at 1:30 PM IST
Where: ACA-VDCA Cricket Stadium, Visakhapatnam

What to expect: Clear skies for starters. In the last ODI played here, Australia bowled India out for just 117. But the preceding two ODIs - both between India and West Indies were high-scoring.

Team Changes

South Africa: Ottneil Baartman and Ryan Rickelton replace Nandre Burger and Tony de Zorzi.

India: Tilak Varma comes in for Washington Sundar.
South Africa Playing XI: Ryan Rickelton, Quinton de Kock (wk), Temba Bavuma, Matthew Breetzke, Aiden Markram (c), Dewald Brevis, Corbin Bosch, Marco Jansen, Keshav Maharaj, Lungi Ngidi, Ottneil Baartman
India Playing XI: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, Ruturaj Gaikwad, Tilak Varma, KL Rahul (c), Ravindra Jadeja, Harshit Rana, Kuldeep Yadav, Arshdeep Singh, Prasidh Krishna
FUN FACT: India have now won the toss after losing in 20 consecutive ODIs - a run that started with the 2023 World Cup final in Ahmedabad.
Temba Bavuma (South Africa's Skipper): "Yeah, we would‚Äôve bowled first as well. The wicket doesn‚Äôt look the easiest, so the plan is simple - start well upfront, assess conditions early, and set things up for the middle order. If we can put a competitive score on the board, we back ourselves to defend it.

It‚Äôs been a really entertaining series, from the intensity of red-ball cricket to the excitement of the white-ball format. The crowd‚Äôs been fantastic in every game, and we definitely want to put in a performance worthy of that support. Hopefully, today turns out to be another thriller.

We‚Äôve got two changes today - Ryan Rickelton and Ottniel Baartman come into the XI. Unfortunately, Nandre Burger and Tony de Zorzi picked up injuries in the last ODI, so they‚Äôll be out for a couple of weeks. But it‚Äôs another opportunity for the guys coming in, and we back them to step up."

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

Here is the teams list that will participate in the next T20 World Cup 2026.

T20 World Cup 2026 teams and groups

Group D: South Africa, New Zealand, Afghanistan, UAE, Canada. India vs Pakistan T20 Cricket World Cup Match Will be played on February 15 2026.

India Playing XI: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, Ruturaj Gaikwad, Tilak Varma, KL Rahul (c), Ravindra Jadeja, Harshit Rana, Kuldeep Yadav, Arshdeep Singh, Prasidh Krishna
FUN FACT: India have now won the toss after losing in 20 consecutive ODIs - a run that started with the 2023 World Cup final in Ahmedabad.
Temba Bavuma (South Africa's Skipper): "Yeah, we would‚Äôve bowled first as well. The wicket doesn‚Äôt look the easiest, so the plan is simple - start well upfront, assess conditions early, and set things up for the middle order. If we can put a competitive score on the board, we back ourselves to defend it.

It‚Äôs been a really entertaining series, from the intensity of red-ball cricket to the excitement of the white-ball format. The crowd‚Äôs been fantastic in every game, and we definitely want to put in a performance worthy of that support. Hopefully, today turns out to be another thriller.

We‚Äôve got two changes today - Ryan Rickelton and Ottniel Baartman come into the XI. Unfortunately, Nandre Burger and Tony de Zorzi picked up injuries in the last ODI, so they‚Äôll be out for a couple of weeks. But it‚Äôs another opportunity for the guys coming in, and we back them to step up."

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

snippet.title: I Got Hunted By the Minecraft LAW
snippet.description:
im innocent dawg (aside from those 1000 players)

I Got Hunted By the Minecraft LAW

minor spoilers below

featuring: @Spokeishere @4CVIT @minutetechmc @PrinceZam @MapiccMc @Leowook @JadenMAN 

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!) 
https://www.youtube.com/@andreaszoeller (all of the minecraft OST remixes are by him!)
https://www.youtube.com/@DMDOKURO (evil void song when spoke shows up..)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, official enderal soundtrack, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

Enderal Soundtrack (HQ): Bone Hunter - Knochenj√§ger https://youtu.be/LchGhXSXxZk by Marvin Kopp, licensed under CC BY 4.0 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

snippet.description:
WWE 2K25 Custom Matches LIVE brings nonstop action, chaos, and entertainment for all wrestling fans who love extreme fights, dream matchups, and over-the-top gameplay! In this live stream, we are showcasing the most insane WWE 2K25 custom matches, including Extreme Rules, Falls Count Anywhere, Hell in a Cell, Cage Match, Iron Man, and many more. With upgraded physics, smoother animations, and powerful new moves, WWE 2K25 delivers the most realistic wrestling experience ever seen in a WWE game.

In this stream, you will see custom superstars, custom arenas, custom championships, and dream matches that are impossible in real WWE. We are combining legendary superstars, current roster stars, and fan-favorite CAWs from Community Creations to create unique match cards that you won‚Äôt find anywhere else. Whether you love hardcore matches, funny glitches, brutal finishers, or dramatic storylines, this WWE 2K25 gameplay has something for everyone.

We will run simulation matches, AI vs AI fights, player vs AI gameplay, and some unpredictable special rules matches designed to test animation limits and physics in WWE 2K25. Expect OMG moments, table breaks, crazy ladders, suplex chains, high-flying maneuvers, dramatic kickouts, and finishers that will shock you. WWE 2K25‚Äôs updated mechanics make every fight feel dynamic and explosive.

This stream will feature superstars like Roman Reigns, Seth Rollins, Cody Rhodes, Brock Lesnar, Randy Orton, LA Knight, CM Punk, John Cena, Undertaker, The Rock, and many more legends & current stars. The women‚Äôs division also brings intense matchups with Rhea Ripley, Becky Lynch, Charlotte Flair, Bianca Belair, and top CAWs.

We will also test out custom-made arenas, championship belts, and story-based rivalries created inside Universe Mode and Custom Match rules. From bloodline wars to fantasy battles, every match is designed for entertainment and high engagement.

If you love WWE games, live streams, Hindi commentary, extreme matches, or just watching destruction, you are in the right place. Stay tuned for new WWE 2K25 videos, shorts, custom match cards, pay-per-view recreations, and special challenge episodes. üíî ‚ÄúAji Rati Gale Pahi Jaliba Mo Jui‚Äù is a heart-touching Odia sad song that reflects the pain of separation, unspoken feelings, and emotional heartbreak sang by Humane Sagar. The soulful voice and emotional lyrics beautifully bring out the depth of love that has been lost, making this track relatable for anyone who has experienced sadness in love.The song captures the journey of someone who still cherishes their beloved (Jui ‚Äì meaning the light of life) even after distance and destiny have created a painful gap. Its melody, music arrangement, and emotional expression make it a powerful sad song that stays with listeners long after it ends.

snippet.title: Case - Official Video | Chandra Brar FT Deepak Dhillon | Gaiphy | New Punjabi song
snippet.description:
Chandra Brar presents ‚ÄòCase‚Äô ‚Äì "Gagsta Soul, Goofy Hard"

Song- Case
Singer- Chandra Brar feat Deepak Dhillon
Female Lead- Samridhi Puri
Lyrics & Composer- Chandra Brar
Music- Gaiphy
Mix/Master- Sameer Charegaonkar
DOP- Harry Saini
Edit- Bhullar Editing Studio
Poster- MG Visuals
Female Costumes- Label Parul Prabhakar

Directed by The Mohit Bawa

Associate Director- Vansh Gumti
Directions Team - Arvi Sandhu, Maan Singh
Making- Ritik Kataria
Line Producer- Amandeep Singh, Davinder Singh
Co Artists- Gurshaan, Sekhon Noorpuri, Tejpal, Baaz, Gur Mand, Harjeet Dhaliwal, Davinder Singh, Param Kanda, Sharry Kanda, Akash Maur, Komal Bhullar, Harjot, 
Project by- Adab Entertainment, Karanvirr
Produced by- Buta Brar
Online Promotion- Vibeline Media
Special Thanks -D.P Transport , Oxbridge School, Rishi School, Sidhu Tailor, Jaspal Sekhon nd Kotapura Police nd Kotkapura citizens 

Song Lyrics:

Kehda bolu vehm jya kadd de
Hun darna durna shad de,
Tu hath jihda ae fadya ohda hath cop na fad de,
Independent artist te teri mukhtyari ni,
Fukri fakri marya kar teri Jatt nale sabji bna yari ni,
Fukri vadu marya Kar ter Jatt nal yaari ni

Ki Shakya lal ter akh ve
Kahdi lad di a tenu makh ve,
Kahnu dab vich tangi firda tera lag jana ae lakh ve,
Kehdi gall to tidya firda ae das yara ve,
Koi Case pawake bethenga lagdai Dildara ve,
Dhara lagwa k bethenga lagdai Dildara ve

Teri age kude a eni mere nal jine a rehnde,
Sada vairi na koi band da asi aap ja k aan khehnde,
Ohda na koi ilaj kre jihde satt mari ni,
Hye Fukri fakri marya kar ter jatt nal yari ni

Hadd tutt jane jiwe taare
Ve tenu honi vaajan maare,
Kal opre chehre sunya puchde collage tere bare,
Utto sunya main policia da hath hunda bhara ve,
Koi Case pawake bethenga lagdai Dildara ve

Tu pawe soota te booti ni jatt balliye gema paunda,
Tera yaar choti da rader a inj balliye hath ni aunda,
Goli wangu sun jandi thapi patt mari ni,
Fukri fakri marya Kar teri jatt nal yaari ni

Ki favourite ae rang thoda ghumde o ehde daale,
Asla feem te rehnde khunde Sadhan rakh lye kale,
Main sunya utto velly ne ve tere Kotkapure wale,
Kyo naam varge kam krda ae Chandre Brara ve,
Koi Case pawake bethenga lagdai Dildara ve


#case #chandrabrar #newpunjabisong
